{"tid":1131730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"讓媽媽放心購物！日本商業大樓提供「寄放爸爸」服務","createTime":"2019-04-30T00:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T03:39:22.000Z","uid":32511,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"705ad0e860292b4d494f92231750cb6a377e4b35","tid":1131730,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:23:54.000Z","msg":"日本從4月27日開始連放十天連假至5月6日，不過連假期間人潮擁擠，大阪難波的商業鬧區一棟辦公大樓，竟然趁勢推出了「寄放爸爸」服務，讓媽媽們可以盡情購物，爸爸與小孩也能有地方休息。<br />\n <br />\n據《朝日新聞》報導，位於辦公大樓內的租賃會議室「難波御堂筋Hall」利用了多餘空間，除了提供可以隨意躺臥的墊子外，也準備了DVD給兒童觀賞。費用為成人1小時500日圓（約新台幣140元），將持續至連假結束為止。<br />\n <br />\n一名受訪的40歲爸爸守田利基和他5歲的兒子，就在媽媽購物時被寄放在此，爸爸還表示，「能夠坐下休息太好了」，會議室的負責人則說，「媽媽也可以前來利用此服務」。"},{"pid":"a268954a0ff8b4e2adad16041e165d783123a130","tid":1131730,"uid":112813,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:25:29.000Z","msg":"有冇姐姐照顧埋爸爸先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5248dacd93d648497ee96835381edea2d2652dd","tid":1131730,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:26:16.000Z","msg":"其實係飛機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eacb55b5d73a6af99ba39327381ee5a0974516de","tid":1131730,"uid":17641,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:27:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>爸爸緊係去飛田新地叫雞喇</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d869aac3465d00b3cd79c8ddce1df7da913ec29","tid":1131730,"uid":67332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:28:41.000Z","msg":"呢鋪仆街，冇人阻止老母買野，一日就爆硬卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155e1bfd6a7aff8bdbc0d3cf